[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "line": 22,
    "target_en": "\\\"All right, it's lunchtime!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 2,
    "line": 25,
    "target_en": " Hey, Rena, put our desks together!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 3,
    "line": 35,
    "target_en": "\\\"Ahahahaha. My lunch has meat balls today!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 4,
    "line": 45,
    "target_en": "\\\"Sounds good!"
  },
  {
    "id": 5,
    "line": 48,
    "target_en": " This ol' man will have some, then."
  },
  {
    "id": 6,
    "line": 51,
    "target_en": " Rika-chan, bring your desk over.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 7,
    "line": 61,
    "target_en": "\\\"......I'm coming."
  },
  {
    "id": 8,
    "line": 64,
    "target_en": " Whoosh☆.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 9,
    "line": 74,
    "target_en": "\\\"Ho ho ho!"
  },
  {
    "id": 10,
    "line": 77,
    "target_en": " Unfortunately, meat balls are my favorite too!"
  },
  {
    "id": 11,
    "line": 80,
    "target_en": " I won't allow you to have any!!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 12,
    "line": 90,
    "target_en": "\\\"Unfortunately, I won't let you do that either, Satoko. "
  },
  {
    "id": 13,
    "line": 97,
    "target_en": "You have to have some veggies, so I cooked some squash for you.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 14,
    "line": 107,
    "target_en": "\\\"Whoa, that's harsh, Shion.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 15,
    "line": 116,
    "target_en": "\\\"Whaaah...... I hate squash!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 16,
    "line": 119,
    "target_en": " Whaah!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 17,
    "line": 125,
    "target_en": "\\\"Don't be so picky about your food! "
  },
  {
    "id": 18,
    "line": 132,
    "target_en": "Squash is very nutritious."
  },
  {
    "id": 19,
    "line": 135,
    "target_en": " You're still growing, so you need to think about things like that. "
  },
  {
    "id": 20,
    "line": 142,
    "target_en": "As long as I live, I won't let you have an unbalanced diet. "
  },
  {
    "id": 21,
    "line": 150,
    "target_en": "Here guys, have some. Steamed squash is delicious.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 22,
    "line": 158,
    "target_en": "\\\"......Munch, munch."
  },
  {
    "id": 23,
    "line": 161,
    "target_en": " Satoko, it's really sweet.\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 24,
    "line": 170,
    "target_en": "\\\"Yeah, it's super good!"
  },
  {
    "id": 25,
    "line": 173,
    "target_en": " The balance of flavors is perfect!"
  },
  {
    "id": 26,
    "line": 176,
    "target_en": " Satoko, don't eat this. It's too good for you!!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 27,
    "line": 186,
    "target_en": "\\\"E-Excuse me?!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 28,
    "line": 189,
    "target_en": " I don't like your tone!!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 29,
    "line": 199,
    "target_en": "\\\"Just try one!"
  },
  {
    "id": 30,
    "line": 202,
    "target_en": " Take a bite!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 31,
    "line": 212,
    "target_en": "\\\"See?"
  },
  {
    "id": 32,
    "line": 215,
    "target_en": " Isn't it good?\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 33,
    "line": 224,
    "target_en": "\\\"......Hmm......"
  },
  {
    "id": 34,
    "line": 229,
    "target_en": " well, it isn't so bad...\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 35,
    "line": 239,
    "target_en": "\\\"Of course it isn't."
  },
  {
    "id": 36,
    "line": 242,
    "target_en": " I've been working hard every day to get you to overcome your dislike of squash. "
  },
  {
    "id": 37,
    "line": 250,
    "target_en": "Okay, now that that's done with, why don't you overcome your fear of eggplants,"
  },
  {
    "id": 38,
    "line": 255,
    "target_en": " green peppers,"
  },
  {
    "id": 39,
    "line": 260,
    "target_en": " and asparagus within the year?\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 40,
    "line": 269,
    "target_en": "\\\"Stop joking!!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 41,
    "line": 272,
    "target_en": " At this rate, I'll transfer to a school in Okinomiya!!!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 42,
    "line": 281,
    "target_en": "\\\"Come on!"
  },
  {
    "id": 43,
    "line": 284,
    "target_en": " I'm in charge of your health, since Satoshi-kun asked me to take care of you."
  },
  {
    "id": 44,
    "line": 287,
    "target_en": " I won't let you eat junk food, either!\\\""
  },
  {
    "id": 45,
    "line": 296,
    "target_en": "\\\"Whaaaah, I hate you, Shion-san!!"
  },
  {
    "id": 46,
    "line": 299,
    "target_en": " I hate squash!!!\\\""
  }
]